Package edu.du.penrose.systems.fedora.client

This package contains classes for accessing the Fedora distribution admin client.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Administrator This is a replacement for the Fedora Distribution class fedora.client.Admininstator with the swing code and static variables removed (so that a GUI client does not start up, when it is instantiated).
Downloader THIS CLASS IS ALMOST AN EXACT COPY OF fedora.client.Downloader.
SwingWorker THIS IS AN EXACT COPY OF fedora.client.SwingWorker, which uses the above copyright and license.
Uploader THIS CLASS IS ALMOST AN EXACT COPY OF fedora.client.Downloader, which uses the above copyright and license.
